data.description: Welcome to your new home! This captivating residence is now on the market in Hillcrest Ranch. Boasting a split floor-plan, this house comprises three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and spans 1,539 sq ft, complete with an RV gate. As you step inside, the wood-look tile floors, open-concept layout, and abundant natural light greet you, offering a warm and inviting atmosphere. The expansive backyard is perfect for your enjoyment. The primary bedroom features a spacious ensuite bathroom with a separate tub and shower, double sinks, and a generously sized walk-in closet. The roof was replaced in 2019. Conveniently located near schools, shopping centers, and the 101 freeway, this home is a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.
